Explain, Predict, and Take Action with Einstein Discovery

Einstein Discovery augments your business intelligence with statistical modeling and supervised machine learning to identify, surface, and visualize insights into your business data. It uses predictive and prescriptive analysis to predict future outcomes, as well as suggests ways in which you can improve predicted outcomes.
